# Reasons for choosing Angular

1. Angular is more mature and maintained by Google.

1. Built-in [routing]

1. Powerful [cli]

1. Built-in [internalization]

1. Support for dynamic [forms]

1. First-party UI library ([angular-materialUI])

1. Better folder & file structure patterns/esthetics

1. Very helpful (first-party) [browser extension]

1. Built-in Support for Sass

1. http client


[browser extension]: https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/angular-devtools/ienfalfjdbdpebioblfackkekamfmbnh
[cli]: https://angular.dev/tools/cli
[routing]: https://angular.dev/guide/routing
[internalization]: https://angular.dev/guide/i18n
[forms]: https://angular.dev/guide/forms
[angular-materialUI]: https://material.angular.io/
